-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Introdution
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

What is 'FASTINTRO-MAKER' (also called: F.I.M.)?

'F.I.M.' is a Demo/IntroMaker or Letterwriter.
Because of using SystemRoutines of the new Amiga OS2.0, the Mainprogram
(F.I.M.) will only run under Kickstart 2.x.
The final created Intros/Demos are running without problems under
Amiga-Kick 1.2/1.3/2.x (from Cli and Workbench)


FASTINTRO-MAKER V2.2 REQUIRES AMIGA-OS2.0 + ASL.LIBRARY


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Distribution-Info
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

It is allowed to distribute `F.I.M.` in anyway (Disks/BBS`s...), when no
change is made to the original Files.
The following files MUST BE included on/in the Distribution-Disk/Archive.

FastIntroMaker_V2.2
FastIntroMaker_V2.2.info
FastIntroMaker.Document
FastIntroMaker.Document.info
FastIntroMaker.Anleitung
FastIntroMaker.Anleitung.info


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Getting started...
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

You can start 'F.I.M.' by double-clicking on its Workbench-Icon or from
CLI with its Filename. If you`re using `Run FastIntroMaker_V2.2`, you are
able to use your Cli as long as you type `Endcli`.

After loading `F.I.M.`, it will open up a Window with many Gadgets which
will be explained now.


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
GadgetFunctions
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gadget-Name        |  Gadget-Function
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
LOAD NEW TEXT      |  LOAD NEW INTRO-DISPLAYTEXT.
                   |  A new ASCII-Text will be loaded into the Text-Buffer
                   |  and displayed on the right ScreenSide. If the Text
                   |  includes unsupported Chars, a new one must be loaded
                   |  or the current-One must be changed.
                   |
LOAD NEW PICT      |  LOAD NEW BACKGROUND-PICTURE.
                   |  A new Picture with the IFF-Format 320×256 (8Colors)
                   |  will be loaded into the Pic-Buffer and displayed as
                   |  Backgroundpic in the current Intro.
                   |  NOTE: The Pic-Format must be IFF 320×256 (8Colors).
                   |  Other Pic-Formats are not supported in this V2.2
                   |  Version of FastIntroMaker !!!
                   |
LOAD NEW MUSIC     |  LOAD NEW BACKGROUND-MUSIC MODULE. (PROTRACKER)
                   |  A new MusicModule, wich will be played as Background-
                   |  Music will be loaded into the Music-Buffer.
                   |  This MusicModule should be created with PROTRACKER or
                   |  a ClonePrg. and should not be longer as max. 32Kbyte.
                   |  MORE INFORMATIONS TO THIS FUNKTION.... SEE ABOVE !!!
                   |
SAVE CURRENT INTRO |  SAVE THE CURRENT INTRO AS EXECUTABLE FILE.
                   |  The current Intro will be saved as File. All F.I.M.-
                   |  IntroPreferences and maybe a Icon will be included.
                   |
SAVE AS BOOTINTRO  |  SAVE THE CURRENT INTRO AS BOOTINTRO TO DISK.
                   |  The current Intro will be saved as BootIntro incl.
                   |  Bootloader/Bootblock to Disk.
                   |  MORE INFORMATIONS TO THIS FUNKTION.... SEE ABOVE !!!
                   |
TEST INTRO         |  VIEW/RUN THE CURRENT INTRO.
                   |  The current Intro will be viewed including all Prefs
                   |  of F.I.M.
                   |
QUIT               |  QUIT FASTINTROMAKER !!!
                   |  Quit F.I.M. and release all allocated Memory.
                   |
SAVE & QUIT        |  SAVE CURRENT INTRO & QUIT F.I.M.   .
                   |  After saving the current Intro without any Errors,
                   |  F.I.M. will be quited and all Memory will be released.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
FONT.............. |  Changes the Type of the current IntroText-Font.
                   |  (Fonttype: Siesta/Byte/Jinx)
                   |
EXIT.............. |  Changes the Exit-Function of the runnig Intro/Demo.
                   |  (Left/Right MouseButton or JoystickButton)
                   |
FG/BG/NO EFFEKT... |  Select the current Intro-(Sinus)Effect.
                   |  NO BG/FG SINUS = Sinus Effect off.
                   |  F-GROUND SINUS = Sinus Effect to Forderground (Text)
                   |  B-GROUND SINUS = Sinus Effect to Background (Picture)
                   |
INTRO-ICON ON/OFF. |  Here you can select to include a Intro-Icon when
                   |  saving a new Intro/Demo.
                   |
TEXTCOLOR......... |  Select the current Font-Display Colors.
                   |
TEXTSPEED......... |  Set the Text-Display Speed for all Intros/Demos.
                   |
