Supported ASCII-Chars
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Here are all supported ASCII-Chars of F.I.M. V2.2:

A-Z (Uppercase-Lowercase)
-------------------------------------------------------
ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ
abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz

ExtraChars1 / 0-9
-------------------------------------------------------
"![\]^_`{|}~ÄäÜüÖö#$%&'()*+,-./:;<=>?@ß0123456789

ExtraChars2       Key-Combinations          Design/Look
-------------------------------------------------------
     ©                R.ALT + e          COPYRIGHT SIGN
     °                R.ALT + 4               FAT POINT
     ·                R.ALT + 8           SQUARE BORDER
     ±                R.ALT + y           SQUARE FILLED
     ø                R.ALT + o       TRIANGLE/ARROW UP
     µ                R.ALT + u     TRIANGLE/ARROW DOWN
     »                R.ALT + 0    TRIANGLE/ARROW RIGHT
     «                R.ALT + 9     TRIANGLE/ARROW LEFT
     ×                R.ALT + x             LITTLE FACE



